OL,3,C'Skulls started floating up': Woman
OL,4,Cfishes 16 dead cats out of garden pond
OL,6,FLewis Warner met Paula Singleton who
OL,7,Fmade the grim discovery. A warning
OL,8,Fthis article contains upsetting
OL,9,Fdetails, and the images of the dead
OL,10,Fcats are blurred.
OL,12,FA woman has discovered the bodies of
OL,13,F16 dead cats in the pond of an empty
OL,14,Fhouse in Coventry.
OL,16,FPaula Singleton, from Canley, was
OL,17,Fsearching for her own two missing cats
OL,18,Fwhen she discovered them dead in a
OL,19,Fgiant garden pond, with the remains of
OL,20,Fmultiple others.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
