PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780308639
OL,3,C'Skulls started floating up': Woman
OL,4,Cfishes 16 dead cats out of garden pond
OL,6,FShe told ITV Central, "I was
OL,7,Fdistraught, heartbroken, to find them.
OL,9,F"It's not the fact that you've found
OL,10,Fthem dead, it's the fact of how
OL,11,Fthey've died as well.
OL,13,F"When you're a cat owner you know your
OL,14,Fcats don't like water, you know that
OL,15,Fis the worst possible way to die for a
OL,16,Fcat."
OL,18,FHer cat Gingernut went missing first,
OL,19,Ffollowed a few weeks later by Clyde.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780308639
OL,3,C'Skulls started floating up': Woman
OL,4,Cfishes 16 dead cats out of garden pond
OL,6,FShe trawled the pond with a fishing
OL,7,Fnet and got her own cats out, followed
OL,8,Fin the end by the remains of around 16
OL,9,Fdead cats, some of which were just
OL,10,Fskulls.
OL,12,F"As I was getting them out it
OL,13,Fdisturbed the water and the skulls of
OL,14,Fseveral others started floating up,
OL,15,Fthat's when I knew it was a massive
OL,16,Fissue, I think I went into shock and
OL,17,Fjust carried on."
OL,19,FAn RSPCA spokesperson said:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780308639
OL,3,C'Skulls started floating up': Woman
OL,4,Cfishes 16 dead cats out of garden pond
OL,6,F"Our vet did not find evidence of
OL,7,Fskeletal damage, which might indicate
OL,8,Fthe cats had been subjected to
OL,9,Fphysical violence.
OL,11,F"At this stage we have no evidence or
OL,12,Finformation from the public that this
OL,13,Fwas a deliberate attack. It is
OL,14,Fpossible it may have been a tragic
OL,15,Faccident with the cats falling into
OL,16,Fthe water and unable to escape, which
OL,17,Fwere not discovered as the house was
OL,18,Fempty."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
