PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780308639
OL,3,C'Skulls started floating up': Woman
OL,4,Cfishes 16 dead cats out of garden pond
OL,6,FBecause they don't believe there was
OL,7,Fany foul play - post-mortem
OL,8,Fexaminations will only be carried out
OL,9,Fif Paula can raise money privately.
OL,10,FShe has been quoted #300 for each cat.
OL,12,FThe public have helped to raise more
OL,13,Fthan #1000 through an online
OL,14,Ffundraiser, but the RSPCA have told
OL,15,FPaula - they can only hold the cats
OL,16,Funtil Tuesday.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
